Senaino CH340 licensing overview
================================

Copyright (c) Tiago Silva.

This repository branch contains open hardware design files, documentation,
fabrication outputs and educational media for the CH340 variant. Different
parts of the branch are licensed as follows:

1. Hardware design sources and fabrication files

   Applies to:

   - hardware/eagle/
   - hardware/gerbers/
   - hardware/exports/
   - hardware/bom/

   License: CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Strongly Reciprocal
   SPDX identifier: CERN-OHL-S-2.0

   License text:
   https://ohwr.org/cern_ohl_s_v2.txt

2. Documentation, photographs, diagrams for teaching use and repository text

   Applies to:

   - README.md
   - CHANGELOG.md
   - CONTRIBUTING.md
   - CITATION.cff
   - .zenodo.json
   - docs/
   - assets/

   License: Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
   SPDX identifier: CC-BY-SA-4.0

   License text:
   https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/legalcode

No warranty
-----------

The design files, documentation and any products made from them are
provided as-is, without warranty of any kind. Users are responsible for
validating the design, fabrication outputs, assembly process and safety
requirements before manufacturing or classroom use.
